{"tid":1662590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抑鬱症係咪唔會好翻","createTime":"2019-10-19T00:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T09:52:08.000Z","uid":152822,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3fa4c55fab9ffae1768af00a6fa80aacdc11b376","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"[好似]好轉咗一排 個人冇咁down<br />\n最近又黎料 <br />\n係咁逼自己接觸一啲自己唔想接觸既野<br />\n控制唔到自己諗咩<br />\n好似係個深坑到無限loop咁<br />\n想永遠都唔醒<br />\n永遠都唔會唔開心"},{"pid":"6f90a1f728611411408f71982d482d3d62310da3","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:52:16.000Z","msg":"依家個人好似得翻個殼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a985fd30a69bd939c7547086918d94794443dbc","tid":1662590,"uid":160964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:52:25.000Z","msg":"唔會，天生的"},{"pid":"167db66848ab4fc396975aa04cc20460f51c7965","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a985fd30a69bd939c7547086918d94794443dbc","tid":1662590,"uid":160964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:52:25.000Z","msg":"唔會，天生的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:54:26.000Z","msg":"細個已經會諗住想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n差在唔敢+怕痛同死唔去"},{"pid":"ff06e731f8c6d7f380dd446dffdea3507abef197","tid":1662590,"uid":318876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"有抑鬱真係好撚慘，仲要對住依個咁病態嘅社會"},{"pid":"9bb4e7a37e3db1450713c1c19a2fd1a0f1467106","tid":1662590,"uid":73804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"我對住個個想自殺啊既人都講<br />\n你要死 都要攬撚住林鄭一齊死<br />\n唔急住死<br />\n人最尾都係會死 而家係辛苦<br />\n但 人最後都係會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f4a17aa286a5ea62d175fc7d3a8981d92ae7bb9","tid":1662590,"uid":312598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:39:37.000Z","msg":"食藥加睇臨床會好啲<br />\n唔好諱疾忌醫呀"},{"pid":"d5373444264d1f325c5f298ba01676d8f91f5b81","tid":1662590,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:50:07.000Z","msg":"會好返 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1020 九龍見"},{"pid":"ae5983a13124ae30aa2bec1a7481c7abb7bf62aa","tid":1662590,"uid":295217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:52:04.000Z","msg":"睇左 I have a black dog未<br />\n會好返的"},{"pid":"7508652a5fe3f6458a6f25d45d599686a72679f3","tid":1662590,"uid":156627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"會<br />\n利申家族遺傳 食咗3年藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"325928a6d258e98f3dcdf3789752b14d16dccf97","tid":1662590,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:54:24.000Z","msg":"留名好返"},{"pid":"eec8882a89e0605381af6b4c88ded4e296a8b621","tid":1662590,"uid":106121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"應該唔會斷尾<br />\n只係時好時壞<br />\n壞果時食藥<br />\n平時做多D運動同鍾意做嘅野<br />\n要慢慢了解下自己對邊方面嘅野容易敏感激動<br />\n避重就輕"},{"pid":"2502ea66bdfed62685e9a4f611bfa4eec1093c42","tid":1662590,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fa4c55fab9ffae1768af00a6fa80aacdc11b376","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"[好似]好轉咗一排 個人冇咁down<br />\n最近又黎料 <br />\n係咁逼自己接觸一啲自己唔想接觸既野<br />\n控制唔到自己諗咩<br />\n好似係個深坑到無限loop咁<br />\n想永遠都唔醒<br />\n永遠都唔會唔開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:16:28.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9oMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=ecb60049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"99a68717276822b77217222e4c6ebc84c7fcafd0","tid":1662590,"uid":290570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"會好返，最好有病徵就食藥或 supplement，無論環境有幾差，只要覺得有希望，就可以捱過。"},{"pid":"b3ebc8f1d738415f9c2968433967e1071a341345","tid":1662590,"uid":288300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:48:52.000Z","msg":"好少會斷尾，但係好多人都可以同個病好好咁共存。最緊要有專業人士睇住你，慢慢改變自己嘅習慣同心態就可以共存到。"},{"pid":"9d445b26909af27dbd3eef32e379b68a11861017","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff06e731f8c6d7f380dd446dffdea3507abef197","tid":1662590,"uid":318876,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"有抑鬱真係好撚慘，仲要對住依個咁病態嘅社會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:21:47.000Z","msg":"覺得好窒息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22459028d242e1db5c021c7d3018d5f874dbe16","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:22:58.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴絲關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3698d470bf8ceee2c59a7c9d046f93e4408506af","tid":1662590,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fa4c55fab9ffae1768af00a6fa80aacdc11b376","tid":1662590,"uid":152822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"[好似]好轉咗一排 個人冇咁down<br />\n最近又黎料 <br />\n係咁逼自己接觸一啲自己唔想接觸既野<br />\n控制唔到自己諗咩<br />\n好似係個深坑到無限loop咁<br />\n想永遠都唔醒<br />\n永遠都唔會唔開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd17c161dd4d169d329a30b5a3151cd42cb4f15","tid":1662590,"uid":147047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"試下去享受抑鬱嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bb272af79e5e650e21c97e289d150816d5b607","tid":1662590,"uid":186060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:28:17.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 我都有抑鬱 食完藥好咗好多"},{"pid":"0e888b2c319e012799d45e5b4f9163735dd3c621","tid":1662590,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:33:14.000Z","msg":"我另一半一路食藥 ( 開心藥+安眠藥 ) 左幾年, 工就繼續番, 問題唔會太大, 唔需要害怕食藥. 要成日提佢唔好 looping, 唔好將所有問題炒埋一碟.<br />\n唔食藥成日會有 panic attack, 出門口前會用手機影晒所有水電野, 有時特登行出門口幾步, 然後再入番去屋企 check 多次, 總之順住佢意願做覺得安心就可以, 唔需下下打擊自己呢樣唔做得, 果樣又唔做得. 唔好將事情唸得太複雜, 簡單隨心就可以.  要多d出街, 晒多d太陽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744593639f7c1b782f87e4a627da34bc7f5fe6ef","tid":1662590,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"係唔會好返<br />\n<br />\n所有人同你講既所謂好返<br />\n係指成功用藥物控制病情令你唔跳樓etc<br />\n而完全唔係正常理解上既回復健康狀態"},{"pid":"048c386857d3418fad5f96b89b0406852d2e7eab","tid":1662590,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"如果我話抑鬱症不是一個病，只是一種暫時的狀態<br />\n你信唔信"},{"pid":"df64ece967b02477233e4e135be63b93700e5fa7","tid":1662590,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T06:17:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010747243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.books.com.tw%2Fproducts%2F0010747243&d=hAhx4mZ6jCiP%2Fv5W8BSz9oMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=f36ed7fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.books.com.tw/products/0010747243</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就睇呢本書，<br />\n唔成功都係無幾十蚊，同埋2小時睇書時間"},{"pid":"dcc69ecc33376c947a656df13bd7a8decd5fb821","tid":1662590,"uid":317192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bb4e7a37e3db1450713c1c19a2